{% if page.url != "/" %}
<nav aria-label="breadcrumb" class="container breadcrumb-nav">
  <ol class="breadcrumb-list" style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center;">
    
    <!-- Always Root Home -->
    <li class="breadcrumb-item">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
    </li>

    <!-- Loop through explicit parent trail if provided -->
    {% if breadcrumbs %}
      {% for crumb in breadcrumbs %}
        <li class="breadcrumb-item">
          {# <span class="breadcrumb-separator" aria-hidden="true">/</span> #}
          <a href="{{ crumb.url }}">{{ crumb.title }}</a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    
    <!-- Fallback for 2-tier service pages with parentTitle/parentUrl -->
    {% elif parentTitle and parentUrl %}
      <li class="breadcrumb-item">
        {# <span class="breadcrumb-separator" aria-hidden="true">/</span> #}
        <a href="{{ parentUrl }}">{{ parentTitle }}</a>
      </li>
    {% endif %}

    <!-- Current Page (No link, marked active) -->
    <li class="breadcrumb-item breadcrumb-current" aria-current="page">
      {# <span class="breadcrumb-separator" aria-hidden="true">/</span> #}
      <span>{{ breadcrumbTitle or serviceName or title }}</span>
    </li>

  </ol>
</nav>
{% endif %}







{# 


How to Configure Your Frontmatter
A. For Top-Level Pages (e.g., /contact-us)
No parent needed! It renders cleanly as: Home / Contact Us

Markdown
---
layout: base.njk
title: Contact Us
permalink: /contact-us/
---



B. For Service Pages (e.g., /masonry-hardscapes)
Set parentTitle and parentUrl. It renders as: Home / Services / Masonry & Hardscapes

Markdown
---
layout: base.njk
title: Masonry & Hardscapes
parentTitle: Services
parentUrl: /services/
permalink: /masonry-hardscapes/
---


C. For Deep-Link / Sub-Service Pages (e.g., /masonry-hardscapes/retaining-walls)
Pass the breadcrumbs array for multiple levels. It renders as: Home / Services / Masonry & Hardscapes / Retaining Walls

Markdown
---
layout: base.njk
title: Retaining Wall Construction
permalink: /masonry-hardscapes/retaining-walls/
breadcrumbs:
  - title: Services
    url: /services/
  - title: Masonry & Hardscapes
    url: /masonry-hardscapes/
---
 #}





















